#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:38
msgid "Respawn Anchor"
msgstr "重生锚"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:48
msgid ""
"The respawn anchor is a block that allows the player to set their spawn "
"point in the Nether. It will only work if fueled using glowstone blocks."
msgstr ""
"重生锚是一种可让玩家在下界设置重生点的方块。只有在使用萤石块充能后，它才能生"
"效。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:49
msgid "Use a glowstone block to add a charge."
msgstr "使用萤石块为其充能。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:50
msgid ""
"Respawn anchors can be charged up to four times. Rightclick on a charged "
"anchor to set a new spawn point."
msgstr "重生锚最多可储存 4 格充能。对已充能的重生锚右键即可设置新的重生点。"

#: mods/ITEMS/mcl_beds/respawn_anchor.lua:51
msgid ""
"A respawn anchor only works in the Nether. Attempting to use a charged "
"anchor to set a new spawn point outside the Nether will cause it to explode."
msgstr ""
"重生锚仅能在下界中使用。在下界之外尝试使用已充能的重生锚来设置新的重生点会导"
"致其爆炸。"
